Package character

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attribute
    Characteristics and settings for attributes in character.
    AttributeModifier
    If items and/or buffs modify attributes it is handled in this class.
    Character
    Where a character essentially is created with all basic statistics and info.
    Inventory
    Managing the inventory of the player.
    ItemSlot
    Wrapper class for item, contains how many exists in the player inventory.
    Skill
    Characteristics and settings for skills in a character.
    SkillModifier
    If buffs modify skills it is handled in this class.
    Spell
    Creates spell and handles getters
    SpellBook
    Contains a list of all the spells the character owns.
    Vital
    Where Vitals are created and modified.
